---
// Sección de servicios Tony Ciencia — 3 ofertas principales
---

<section class="services-section" id="servicios" aria-labelledby="services-heading">
	<div class="services-inner">
		<div class="services-header">
			<p class="services-eyebrow">Lo que ofrezco</p>
			<h2 id="services-heading" class="services-title">
				Elige cómo quieres aprender
			</h2>
		</div>

		<div class="services-grid">
			<!-- Servicio 1: Curso n8n -->
			<article class="service-card card-featured">
				<div class="service-icon">
					<svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
						<path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07A19.5 19.5 0 0 1 4.69 13a19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 3.6 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.127.96.361 1.903.7 2.81a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.907.339 1.85.573 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<div class="service-badge">Más popular</div>
				<h3 class="service-title">Master Automation con n8n</h3>
				<p class="service-desc">
					Aprende a automatizar cualquier proceso de negocio a tu ritmo. Workflows reales, casos prácticos y soporte de la comunidad.
				</p>
				<ul class="service-features">
					<li>Curso autoguiado a tu ritmo</li>
					<li>Plantillas de workflows listos</li>
					<li>Comunidad de estudiantes</li>
					<li>Acceso de por vida</li>
				</ul>
				<a href="/pages/cursos" class="service-cta service-cta-primary">
					Ver el curso →
				</a>
			</article>

			<!-- Servicio 2: Mentoría 1:1 -->
			<article class="service-card">
				<div class="service-icon">
					<svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
						<path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="service-title">Mentoría 1:1</h3>
				<p class="service-desc">
					Sesión personalizada de 60 minutos en Zoom con Antonio Duque. Resuelve tus dudas y avanza más rápido con tu proyecto.
				</p>
				<ul class="service-features">
					<li>60 minutos vía Zoom</li>
					<li>Revisión de tu caso real</li>
					<li>Plan de acción personalizado</li>
					<li>Grabación incluida</li>
				</ul>
				<a href="/pages/mentoria" class="service-cta service-cta-secondary">
					Reservar sesión →
				</a>
			</article>

			<!-- Servicio 3: Agencia IA -->
			<article class="service-card">
				<div class="service-icon">
					<svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
						<rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="service-title">Agencia IA Full-Stack</h3>
				<p class="service-desc">
					Soluciones de IA y automatización a medida para tu empresa. Integramos n8n, Make, OpenAI y más en tus procesos existentes.
				</p>
				<ul class="service-features">
					<li>Análisis de procesos actuales</li>
					<li>Desarrollo a medida</li>
					<li>Soporte y mantenimiento</li>
					<li>Empresas en USA, LATAM y Europa</li>
				</ul>
				<a href="/pages/agencia" class="service-cta service-cta-secondary">
					Hablar con nosotros →
				</a>
			</article>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.services-section {
		background: #0a0c12;
		padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
	}

	.services-inner {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.services-header {
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}

	.services-eyebrow {
		font-size: 0.8125rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		color: #06b6d4;
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
	}

	.services-title {
		font-family: var(--font-display, var(--font-sans));
		font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
		font-weight: 800;
		color: #f1f5f9;
		letter-spacing: -0.03em;
		line-height: 1.15;
	}

	.services-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
		gap: 1.5rem;
	}

	.service-card {
		position: relative;
		background: rgba(22, 25, 34, 0.7);
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);
		border-radius: 16px;
		padding: 2rem;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1rem;
		transition: border-color 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
	}

	.service-card:hover {
		border-color: rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.3);
		transform: translateY(-4px);
	}

	.card-featured {
		border-color: rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.3);
		background: rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.07);
	}

	.card-featured:hover {
		border-color: rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.6);
	}

	.service-icon {
		width: 52px;
		height: 52px;
		border-radius: 12px;
		background: rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.15);
		border: 1px solid rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.2);
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		color: #a78bfa;
	}

	.service-badge {
		position: absolute;
		top: 1.25rem;
		right: 1.25rem;
		padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
		background: rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.2);
		border: 1px solid rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.3);
		border-radius: 100px;
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: #c4b5fd;
	}

	.service-title {
		font-family: var(--font-display, var(--font-sans));
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: #f1f5f9;
		line-height: 1.3;
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
	}

	.service-desc {
		font-size: 0.9375rem;
		color: #64748b;
		line-height: 1.6;
		flex: 1;
	}

	.service-features {
		list-style: none;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.5rem;
	}

	.service-features li {
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		color: #94a3b8;
		padding-left: 1.25rem;
		position: relative;
	}

	.service-features li::before {
		content: "✓";
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		color: #10b981;
		font-weight: 700;
		font-size: 0.75rem;
	}

	.service-cta {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		padding: 0.625rem 1.25rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		font-size: 0.9375rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: background 0.15s ease, transform 0.15s ease;
		margin-top: 0.5rem;
		width: fit-content;
	}

	.service-cta-primary {
		background: #7c3aed;
		color: white;
	}

	.service-cta-primary:hover {
		background: #6d28d9;
		transform: translateX(2px);
		color: white;
	}

	.service-cta-secondary {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		color: #cbd5e1;
	}

	.service-cta-secondary:hover {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		transform: translateX(2px);
		color: #e2e8f0;
	}

	@media (max-width: 900px) {
		.services-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			max-width: 480px;
			margin: 0 auto;
		}
	}
</style>
